WILLIAM & MARY
CHARTERED 1693

HERBARIUM OF THE COLLEGE OF
WILLIAM AND MARY
Williamsburg, Virginia
VIRGINIA

Gloucester Co.                                                     19 May 1977
*Galax aphylla* L.

Several colonies along shaded N-facing
*Kalmia* thickets at Leigh's Pond, in as-
sociation with *Epigaea repens*. Only 2
flowering stalks seen from over 300 plants
in one largest colony. I-5. Rare.

Collector: James M Greaves
Pamela H Wilson
John T Deal                                                      No. 1549

28456
